Class IdGraph<G extends IdGraph<G>>

  • java.lang.Object

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public class IdGraph<G extends IdGraph<G>>
extends Object
implements com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers.WrapperGraph<com.tinkerpop.blueprints.KeyIndexableGraph>, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.KeyIndexableGraph, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.IndexableGraph, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.TransactionalGraph
    A KeyIndexableGraph able to map the result of each method call to a dedicated implementation.

    Re-implemented from com.tinkerpop.blueprints.util.wrappers.id.IdGraph.
